{"tid":265274,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新盜墓迷城 ＆ 黑暗宇宙討論區","createTime":"2017-05-31T13:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T11:41:51.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e315b687c83b0953678582687fa3c70900dc2de","tid":265274,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"湯告魯斯新版《盜墓迷城》一早已被確認為環球影業「怪物電影宇宙」嘅起點，今日環球影業公布該系列定名為《Dark Universe》，主角包括《盜墓迷城》內出現、由羅素高爾所飾演嘅變身怪醫Dr Henry Jekyll；據之前消息所指，Dr Jekyll將會負責串連各部作品。<br />\n另外兩位重量級（怪物）登場角色係由尊尼特普所飾嘅隱形人（The Invisible Man），以及哈維亞巴頓飾演嘅科學怪人（Frankenstein），而女星蘇菲亞寶迪拉就係喺《盜墓迷城》預告中亮相嘅木乃伊妖后。其他未公布演員嘅角色仲有德古拉伯爵（Dracula）、半魚人（Black Lagoon）及人狼（Wolfman）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2017/05/dark-universe.jpg?w=560\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimedotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fdark-universe.jpg%3Fw%3D560&h=47d914cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n呢張相會否表示Johnny depp同 javier bardem會客串the mummy？？<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個宇宙都有佢特色，就係從來無人想過原來呢d妖怪存在一個世界會點，但同時無咩認識既人"},{"pid":"c24626bb0e41fba4bc0c46ce593bf8b5adf24c96","tid":265274,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"點解套野個名直接用返盜墓迷城,改都唔改下?"},{"pid":"a7dae052f9916fc216eadc6130222f550715c607","tid":265274,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>湯告魯斯新版《盜墓迷城》一早已被確認為環球影業「怪物電影宇宙」嘅起點，今日環球影業公布該系列定名為《Dark Universe》，主角包括《盜墓迷城》內出現、由羅素高爾所飾演嘅變身怪醫Dr Henry Jekyll；據之前消息所指，Dr Jekyll將會負責串連各部作品。<br />\n另外兩位重量級（怪物）登場角色係由尊尼特普所飾嘅隱形人（The Invisible Man），以及哈維亞巴頓飾演嘅科學怪人（Frankenstein），而女星蘇菲亞寶迪拉就係喺《盜墓迷城》預告中亮相嘅木乃伊妖后。其他未公布演員嘅角色仲有德古拉伯爵（Dracula）、半魚人（Black Lagoon）及人狼（Wolfman）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2017/05/dark-universe.jpg?w=560\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimedotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fdark-universe.jpg%3Fw%3D560&h=47d914cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n呢張相會否表示Johnny depp同 javier bardem會客串the mummy？？<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個宇宙都有佢特色，就係從來無人想過原來呢d妖怪存在一個世界會點，但同時無咩認識既人</blockquote><br />\n同時對無咩認識既人都要想方法話俾佢地知係可以咁做，唔同marvel同dc本身已經有漫畫世界存在"},{"pid":"e21b9fc57d860daef31064bf36e822ba46a65350","tid":265274,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解套野個名直接用返盜墓迷城,改都唔改下?</blockquote><br />\nrobocop都係，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"e0b261cee5674ffda5b7a0038c792e535c59f338","tid":265274,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"舊版正好多  好探險feel"},{"pid":"51c7edc22b384fd0e2f92af9ea6b53c41c3ad9bf","tid":265274,"uid":35313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:51:19.000Z","msg":"職業特工隊：特務迷城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e77db2e6038a524ef734d2edd03a14f55bc93d","tid":265274,"uid":3567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解套野個名直接用返盜墓迷城,改都唔改下?</blockquote><br />\nrobocop都係，大家點睇？</blockquote><br />\n因為原祖舊版193幾年個套都係叫mummy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n99年個套都係remake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a51d280f3cdda063218204ca900f8b21041392","tid":265274,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:58:31.000Z","msg":"搵Hugh Jackman做wolfman?"},{"pid":"3fa620c910e5a6145bd1a0d1fac303832d45f440","tid":265274,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職業特工隊：特務迷城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />mi 太洗腦"},{"pid":"e401000ecd257f92c5579ea15b196fc315885d7a","tid":265274,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl